The White House is inviting volunteers to help decorate, perform, and greet guests during the holiday season. Applications are now open and will close on October 19th, 2022. The White House welcomes submissions from all U.S. states and territories and encourages military family members, educators, frontline workers, and students to apply. Volunteers must be available in Washington, D.C. during the designated timeframes. COVID-19 safety measures will be in place, and the White House reserves the right to adjust availability based on health guidance. For more information, interested individuals can reach out to Volunteers@who.eop.gov.